Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.53,0:02:18.78,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}接下來到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.20,0:02:22.74,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}玩膩了打發時間的遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.83,0:02:26.25,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}反正也是犧牲品吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.41,0:02:30.04,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}我是我的世界的王
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.04,0:02:33.38,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}在水面上也能跑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.71,0:02:37.38,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H414141&\3a&H82&}掉在地上的蛋也能逆再生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.38,0:02:40.76,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H414141&\3a&H82&}甚至能成為宇航員
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.93,0:02:44.47,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H414141&\3a&H82&}從天而落的珠子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.64,0:02:48.02,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}撿拾收集起來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.27,0:02:52.06,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}終有一天 能去到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.11,0:02:55.19,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}能豎起只屬於自己的自由之旗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.53,0:02:59.11,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}穿著滿是破洞的旅遊鞋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.11,0:03:02.66,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}在穿堂風中強忍淚水
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.82,0:03:06.91,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}深呼出一兩口氣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.00,0:03:09.87,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}站起來吧拳擊手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.12,0:03:13.67,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}起死回生的機會只有一次
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.75,0:03:17.09,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}敲響畫中的門
