Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.13,0:23:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.45,0:23:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀 麵包圈！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.21,0:23:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你買了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.89,0:23:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,還有點熱呢 是剛炸好的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.66,0:23:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,麵包圈 我想吃
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.89,0:23:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,真想趁熱吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.00,0:23:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,但吃過以後就吃不下晚飯了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.66,0:23:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,日向還沒回來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.25,0:23:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,好晚
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.02,0:23:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,這是啥 我能吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.09,0:23:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,可以嗎 可以吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.94,0:23:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,手好長！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.17,0:23:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,日向正好回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.65,0:23:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.90,0:23:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.86,0:24:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,日向？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.20,0:24:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,是日向吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.70,0:24:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,日向？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.58,0:24:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,小零 姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.23,0:24:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,日向？
